	recursion.  The 'Parent == null' condition isn't sufficient for
	anonymous methods.
	(FlowBranching.AddBreakOrigin): Likewise.
	(FlowBranching.AddContinueOrigin): Likewise.
	(FlowBranching.AddReturnOrigin): Likewise.
