	(ReflectionParameters.ReflectionParameters): Make private.
	(ReflectionParameters.GetConstaints): New factory method.
	* generic.cs (TypeParameterDefineType): Use it.
	(TypeManager.GetTypeParameterConstraints): Likewise.

