	(Constraints.IsSubclassOf): New internal method.

	* typemanager.cs (TypeManager.FindMembers): Added special support
	for GenericTypeParameterBuilder's.	
	(TypeManager.IsSubclassOf, IsFamilyAccessible): Added support for
	type parameters.

