	Committing a patch from Ben Maurer; see bug #50820.

	* typemanager.cs (TypeManager.FilterWithClosure): Added CS1540
	check for classes.

	* ecore.cs (Expression.MemberLookupFailed): Added CS1540 check for
	classes.	

