	is called from DeclSpace's .ctor to add 
	(Namespace.Lookup): Include DeclSpaces in the lookup.

	* class.cs (Operator): Derive from MemberBase, not MemberCore.

	* const.cs (Const): Derive from MemberBase, not MemberCore.	

