	* class.cs (TypeContainer::EmitField): Remove and move into 
	(Field::Define): here and modify accordingly.
	(Field.FieldBuilder): New member.
	(TypeContainer::Populate): Update accordingly.
	(TypeContainer::FindMembers): Implement.

